room_title: Escape room "Spy Trainer" by Exit Strategy in Charlotte
review: My family went on July 25th and did the Spy Trainer room. We had such a blast. Spy Kelley was awesome! From beginning to end, we had a blast!

room_title: Escape room "Spy Trainer" by Exit Strategy in Charlotte
review: My friends and I did Spy Trainer at the North location. It was my first time and I loved it! The staff, Jason and Christy were phenomenal! Thanks so much for making our experience pleasant and memorable!

room_title: Escape room "Spy Trainer" by Exit Strategy in Charlotte
review: This was an amazing experience! I had so much fun with my boyfriend and parents completing The Spy Room. We are officially spies, but we couldn't have done it without our amazing clue master Travis. He was so helpful. I will definitely be coming back!
